            "_key": "k6",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [],
            "text": "Explore Indonesia's most renowned dive destinations, from Raja Ampat, Komodo, and Flores to the Banda Sea, and beyond. Mari Liveaboard is a 30m traditional Indonesian ironwood Phinisi built for serious divers who value comfort, space, and exceptional value."
          }
        ],
        "markDefs": [],
        "style": "normal"
      }
    ],
